azon.co.jp/gp/product/B06X6ND93T |title=\u73fe\u5b9f\u4e3b\u7fa9\u52c7\u8005\u306e\u738b\u56fd\u518d\u5efa\u8a18 3|website=[[Amazon.co.jp]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=May 29, 2019 }}</ref>\n | ISBN            = 978-4-86554-191-5\n | LicensedRelDate = August 3, 2017 (Digital)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://j-novel.club/v/how-a-realist-hero-rebuilt-the-kingdom-volume-3|title=''How a Realist Hero Rebuilt the Kingdom'' Vol. 3 (Digital Version)|website=[[J-Novel Club]]|accessdate=May 29, 2019}}</ref><br>May 28, 2019 (Print)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sevenseasentertainment.com/books/how-a-realist-hero-rebuilt-the-kingdom-light-novel-vol-3/|title=''How a Realist Hero Rebuilt the Kingdom'' Vol. 3 (Print Version)|website=[[Seven Seas Entertainment]] |accessdate=May 29, 2019 }}</ref>\n | LicensedISBN    = 978-1-642750-44-7\n | LineColor       = DB7093\n\n| ChapterList     = \n* Prologue: On a Moonlit Terrace\n* Chapter 1: Project Lorelei\n* Intermission 1: Lord Ishizuka\n* Chapter 2: Meeting on a Street Corner in Van\n* Chapter 3: Negotiations\n* Chapter 4: Pact\n| ChapterListCol2 =\n* Chapter 5: Withdrawal\n* ''Extra Story:'' The Story of a Certain Group of Adventurers 3\n* Chapter 6: Standing in Front of the Lion's Cage\n* Chapter 7: Promise\n* Chapter 8: Crime and Punishment\n* Epilogue: Peace is Yet Distant\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n | VolumeNumber    = 4\n | RelDate         = March 15, 2017<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B071G76KMY |title=\u73fe\u5b9f\u4e3b\u7fa9\u52c7\u8005\u306e\u738b\u56fd\u518d\u5efa\u8a18 4|website=[[Amazon.co.jp]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=May 29, 2019}}</ref>\n | ISBN            = 978-4-86554-226-4\n | LicensedRelDate = October 19, 2017 (Digital)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://j-novel.club/v/how-a-realist-hero-rebuilt-the-kingdom-volume-4|title=''How a Realist Hero Rebuilt the Kingdom'' Vol. 4 (Digital Version)|website=[[J-Novel Club]]|accessdate=May 29, 2019}}</ref><br>September 17, 2019 (Print)<ref>{{cite web |url